  "title": "CLASS 4 DRIVER",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p><ul><li>Ensure timely delivery of goods in accordance to assign schedule.</li><li>Perform loading and unloading of goods, ensuring goods are safety secured.</li><li>Keeping vehicle in good condition.</li><li>Perform basic maintenance / upkeeping of vehicle.</li><li>Any ad hoc duties as assigned by supervisor.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Lorry Driver with valid Class 4 License.</li><li>Relevant working experience with Logistics Industry will be an advantage.</li></ul><p><strong>Benefit:</strong></p><p>1) Salary: S$2500 + xx allowance (base on conditions)</p><p>2) Overtime & Job Incentives (after target)</p><p>3) Location:</p><ul><li>If candidate stays in West, they will report to Gul Way</li><li>If Central, Keppel area</li><li>If East, 10 Ubi Crescent</li></ul><p>4) If candidate stays nearby to below parking areas, they can drive the vehicle home:</p><ul><li>Bulim Ave</li><li>Marsiling Crescent</li><li>Eunos</li><li>Tampines North Beside Giant</li><li>Jalan Boon Lay</li></ul><p>5) Annual Leave: 12 + 2</p><p>6) Workdays: 5.5</p><p>7) Timing: 8.30am to 5.30pm (Monday to Friday), 8.30am to 12.30pm (Saturday)</p><p>Job Types: Full-time, Permanent<br /></p><p>Chan Wei Wen, Mervyn (Reg. No: R25149588)</p><p>ST Venture EmPloyment Agency (EA License No: 09C5583)</p><p>Please send an updated resume to stvea888@gmail.com if you are keen to apply for this position</p>",
